snippet.title: Retro Rockets Coming to Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Retro Rockets is a retro-future multiplayer game where you hunt Retronauts and deorbit space stations as Destructo! Or play as the Retronauts and work together and defend against Destructo by enabling the security systems that will make the killer robot rest in pieces.

Retro Rockets is coming to Kickstarter on 02 April 2019! 

You can already put Retro Rockets on your wishlist on Steam!
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/921890/Retro_Rockets/
